trans-unit.source: Identifies the point properties of a visual style element.
trans-unit.target: 标识的视觉样式元素的点属性。

trans-unit.source: The PointProperty enumeration represents a set of point properties that describe visual style elements.
trans-unit.target: PointProperty 枚举表示一组描述视觉样式元素的点属性。

trans-unit.source: The PointProperty values are used as an argument in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleRenderer.GetPoint%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to specify which property value to retrieve for the element that the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleRenderer> currently represents.
trans-unit.target: PointProperty 值用作中的自变量<xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleRenderer.GetPoint%2A?displayProperty=fullName>方法，以指定要检索的元素的属性值的<xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleRenderer>当前表示。</xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleRenderer> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.VisualStyles.VisualStyleRenderer.GetPoint%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
